headline: GTA Online Update
subtitle: Introducing the new Enus Huntley S
content:
Merging the style and craftsmanship of a classic English luxury motorcar with the feature set of a high-end SUV, the Huntley S might be the only example of British-American fusion that actually works. Or maybe it’s a tasteless mess with a carbon footprint equivalent to a medium sized rain forest. You decide.

Available for purchase now from legendarymotorsport.net and featured in the new High Life race ‘Home in the Hills'.
